{"thig6.4:0.1":"Therigatha 6.4 ","thig6.4:0.2":"Chakkanipata ","thig6.4:0.3":"Sujatatherigatha ","thig6.4:1.1":"“Alankata suvasana, ","thig6.4:1.2":"malini candanokkhita; ","thig6.4:1.3":"Sabbabharanasanchanna, ","thig6.4:1.4":"dasiganapurakkhata. ","thig6.4:2.1":"Annam pananca adaya, ","thig6.4:2.2":"khajjam bhojjam anappakam; ","thig6.4:2.3":"Gehato nikkhamitvana, ","thig6.4:2.4":"uyyanamabhiharayim. ","thig6.4:3.1":"Tattha ramitva kilitva, ","thig6.4:3.2":"agacchanti sakam gharam; ","thig6.4:3.3":"Viharam datthum pavisim, ","thig6.4:3.4":"sakete anjanam vanam. ","thig6.4:4.1":"Disvana lokapajjotam, ","thig6.4:4.2":"vanditvana upavisim; ","thig6.4:4.3":"So me dhammamadesesi, ","thig6.4:4.4":"anukampaya cakkhuma. ","thig6.4:5.1":"Sutva ca kho mahesissa, ","thig6.4:5.2":"saccam sampativijjhaham; ","thig6.4:5.3":"Tattheva virajam dhammam, ","thig6.4:5.4":"phusayim amatam padam. ","thig6.4:6.1":"Tato vinnatasaddhamma, ","thig6.4:6.2":"pabbajim anagariyam; ","thig6.4:6.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","thig6.4:6.4":"amogham buddhasasanan”ti. ","thig6.4:7.1":"… Sujata theri …. "}